## Iana.LanguageSubtags.JarConverters.loadRawSubtagRegistryFromString() function

Parses a text (JAR) format language subtag registry from string content and returns the registry format with field names matching legacy test JSON format ("Suppress-Script", "Preferred-Value").

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare function loadRawSubtagRegistryFromString(content: string): Result<JarModel.RegistryFile>;
```
